  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To demonstrate the superiority of ASP8825 over placebo and dose response in patients with
      painful diabetic polyneuropathy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Three doses of ASP8825 are compared to placebo in efficacy and safety point of view in
      patients with painful diabetic polyneuropathy.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
  <why_stopped>
    An independent DMC determined continuation was unlikely to demonstrate a statistically
    significant advantage of ASP8825 over placebo on the primary endpoint
  </why_stopped>
